# 🍰 Cakelicious – E-commerce Landing Page

Cakelicious is a visually appealing bakery-themed e-commerce landing page designed to showcase cakes and desserts with a soft pastel UI. The project focuses on clean design, smooth user experience, and responsive layout using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

---

## ✨ Features

* 🎂 Attractive product showcase (cakes & desserts)
* 🎨 Soft pastel color palette for a bakery feel
* 🧭 Simple and clean navigation
* 💻 Responsive design (works on different screen sizes)
* 🛒 E-commerce style layout with product cards

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript

---

## 🎯 Purpose

This project is created to demonstrate frontend development and UI/UX design skills by building a real-world inspired bakery e-commerce interface.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

👉 https://mahvishsk.github.io/Cakelicious-Ecommerce-Frontend/

